HTML:- Hyper Text Markup Language

- It is about stating and ending tag.
- It has a Head portion and Body portion    
    - Head have meta data, has tag like meta,title etc.
    - Body have the over all web structure, has tags like header tag(h<n>),paragraph tag(p) etc.
- It has a "DOCTYPE" and a "html" tag which has head and body tag 
